klighting makes info easy to read as ambient light changes, with an eye-protecting display for night riding&#34;,&#34;img&#34;:&#34;assets/images/关键部位图/20190606112906.png&#34;,&#34;number&#34;:&#34;/etc/designs/cfmoto/assets/product/category/04@2x.jpg&#34;},{&#34;title&#34;:&#34;LED Lighting&#34;,&#34;name&#34;:&#34;dot-point4&#34;,&#34;des&#34;:&#34;Pierce the night with all LED lighting on the 650GT. The signature L-shaped light strip is automobile-inspired and offers a modern.sophisticated look. Separated headlights optimize light clarity so you can ride confidently even after the sun goes down.&#34;,&#34;img&#34;:&#34;assets/images/关键部位图/20190606113016.png&#34;,&#34;number&#34;:&#34;/etc/designs/cfmoto/assets/product/category/05@2x.jpg&#34;}]}" variant="[{&#34;image&#34;:&#34;assets/images/650GT 正右侧 骑士黑 .png&#34;,&#34;title&#34;:&#34;Midnight Black &#34;,&#34;desc&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;modelColor&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;colorImage&#34;:&#34;assets/images/Midnight Black.png&#34;},{&#34;image&#34;:&#34;assets/images/CFMOTO-650GT-正右侧-星光白.png&#34;,&#34;title&#34;:&#34;Nebula White&#34;,&#34;desc&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;modelColor&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;colorImage&#34;:&#34;assets/images/Nebula White (1).png&#34;}]"/>
